WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.990
=Episode 19=

01:49.340 --> 01:50.180
Next one.

01:51.340 --> 01:52.180
Yes.

01:56.860 --> 01:58.340
This outfit is splendid

01:58.500 --> 01:59.340
and quite light.

01:59.910 --> 02:01.500
It won't hinder movement at all.

02:04.390 --> 02:05.300
It is good,

02:06.110 --> 02:07.990
but the design is too ornate.

02:08.550 --> 02:09.510
How wise of you.

02:10.020 --> 02:10.990
I think the same way.

02:11.350 --> 02:12.270
Allow me to trim it.

02:17.350 --> 02:18.190
How is it now?

02:19.230 --> 02:20.110
This one will do.

02:20.510 --> 02:21.350
Yes.

02:26.020 --> 02:26.860
Simu,

02:27.230 --> 02:28.180
you want a new outfit?

02:29.230 --> 02:30.230
Sir, do you know

02:30.900 --> 02:32.180
the Void Tournament is near?

02:33.110 --> 02:33.960
I came

02:33.960 --> 02:35.580
to take Her Grace's measure.

02:36.790 --> 02:37.860
What is that?

02:38.900 --> 02:39.900
Every hundred years,

02:40.420 --> 02:41.510
Her Grace holds

02:41.510 --> 02:42.350
a Void Tournament.

02:42.900 --> 02:43.790
On that day,

02:44.300 --> 02:45.740
any spirit can challenge her.

02:46.740 --> 02:47.580
If they win,

02:47.740 --> 02:49.180
Her Grace yields

02:49.510 --> 02:50.350
the throne to them.

02:50.790 --> 02:51.630
And if they lose?

02:52.140 --> 02:52.980
If they lose,

02:55.390 --> 02:56.700
they wait for the next century

02:56.700 --> 02:57.550
and try again.

03:03.420 --> 03:04.460
I see.

03:06.700 --> 03:07.580
No wonder

03:07.580 --> 03:08.740
the city feels different.

03:12.790 --> 03:13.630
Simu,

03:15.620 --> 03:16.830
why hold this tournament?

03:17.210 --> 03:18.070
The desires of spirits

03:18.070 --> 03:19.740
can never be erased.

03:21.110 --> 03:21.990
Rather than curb them,

03:22.270 --> 03:24.110
better let them stir up some trouble.

03:24.990 --> 03:26.020
I can't let them

03:26.020 --> 03:27.110
keep trying to kill me.

03:29.020 --> 03:29.860
But your power

03:30.180 --> 03:31.020
has weakened.

03:31.950 --> 03:32.990
How will you face them?

03:36.580 --> 03:37.420
You can sense

03:37.430 --> 03:38.300
my power change?

03:40.550 --> 03:41.390
I can sense

03:42.830 --> 03:43.700
that you've grown

03:44.830 --> 03:45.700
a little weaker.

03:49.700 --> 03:50.540
It is nothing.

03:51.620 --> 03:53.020
The Fusang Tree is restored.

03:53.830 --> 03:55.510
Next, I need only breath regulation.

03:56.070 --> 03:56.990
I can handle it.

03:58.015 --> 03:59.112
If they find out about that

03:59.123 --> 03:59.963
during the contest,

04:00.860 --> 04:02.460
what will your ambitious courtiers

04:03.300 --> 04:04.140
do then?

04:06.020 --> 04:07.830
Even together, they're no match for me.

04:08.990 --> 04:10.700
But if I don't show up,

04:12.020 --> 04:13.208
they'll immediately figure out

04:13.219 --> 04:13.900
what's going on.

04:15.020 --> 04:15.860
By then,

04:16.740 --> 04:17.710
over half of the spirits

04:17.710 --> 04:18.940
will be after my life.

04:25.590 --> 04:26.430
So,

04:28.990 --> 04:29.830
you have to show up?

04:31.230 --> 04:32.070
That's right.

04:33.030 --> 04:34.110
What would make you not go?

04:36.500 --> 04:37.380
Nothing could stop me.

04:39.260 --> 04:40.300
I'm your spell bearer.

04:40.940 --> 04:41.780
And I can't stop you?

04:43.710 --> 04:45.350
What does that have to do with that?

04:48.620 --> 04:49.460
As for you,

04:50.860 --> 04:51.700
these past few days,

04:52.300 --> 04:54.180
you've been running out every day.

04:54.710 --> 04:56.060
Is the Void that enticing to you?

05:01.150 --> 05:02.260
You're not used

05:03.670 --> 05:04.740
to my absence, right?

05:06.710 --> 05:07.550
Watch your tongue.

05:08.420 --> 05:09.270
I should have let you

05:09.270 --> 05:10.740
keep suffering from cold poison.

05:12.380 --> 05:13.300
Please calm your anger.

05:13.910 --> 05:15.150
I was only joking just now.

05:16.300 --> 05:17.180
I've been going out

05:18.300 --> 05:19.140
for this very thing.

05:37.590 --> 05:38.690
I've troubled you for days,

05:39.277 --> 05:40.610
so I wanted to get you something.

05:41.500 --> 05:42.470
I made this for you.

05:42.470 --> 05:45.500
♪Spring comes; ice and snow thaw♪

05:47.320 --> 05:50.490
♪All things wake, with the east wind♪

05:51.080 --> 05:51.960
I don't want

05:51.970 --> 05:53.420
such a pointless thing.

05:56.340 --> 06:00.110
♪In the season at its fullest♪

06:00.230 --> 06:01.470
I worked very hard on it.

06:02.500 --> 06:03.740
Please accept it, Your Grace.

06:05.480 --> 06:08.270
♪The old night♪

06:12.740 --> 06:19.680
♪Borrow mortal warmth to ease the cold♪

06:20.100 --> 06:27.070
♪Warm winds bring fragrant blooms♪

06:27.350 --> 06:34.350
♪Let me love with all my heart
in youthful grace♪

06:34.630 --> 06:38.100
♪With light, carefree words♪

06:38.290 --> 06:42.970
♪Still shining bright♪

06:45.990 --> 06:47.300
You're recovering quite well.

06:48.030 --> 06:48.870
Soon,

06:49.620 --> 06:50.740
your cold poison will heal.

06:50.950 --> 06:56.080
♪A brief life dares seek eternity♪

06:56.230 --> 06:57.150
But I can sense

06:58.300 --> 06:59.740
you've spent much spirit power again.

06:59.980 --> 07:03.610
♪Borrow one lovely dream♪

07:04.710 --> 07:05.820
Do not probe into me.

07:08.260 --> 07:09.100
I can't do that.

07:09.620 --> 07:10.940
My life depends on you.

07:12.150 --> 07:13.663
If anything happens at the tournament,

07:13.740 --> 07:14.580
I'll lose my shelter,

07:15.230 --> 07:16.700
and the Right Hand will end me first.

07:18.710 --> 07:20.350
At least you know your place.

07:23.100 --> 07:25.780
(Zhaomu Pavilion)

07:25.780 --> 07:31.880
♪I see a ray♪

07:33.990 --> 07:36.570
♪To what home shall I return♪

07:50.860 --> 07:52.380
How boring.

08:08.900 --> 08:09.740
(Gao Xuande, Ji Youming, Xiao Yuan)

08:09.740 --> 08:10.700
(Jun Lin, Yin Lang, Gu Cangwu)

08:14.540 --> 08:15.380
(Yin Lang)

08:15.380 --> 08:16.220
(Jiling Temple)

08:25.170 --> 08:26.143
- Your Ladyship.
- Move.

08:26.350 --> 08:27.190
Move.

08:27.670 --> 08:28.620
Let me go.

08:31.110 --> 08:31.950
Let me go!

08:31.960 --> 08:32.840
Move.

08:34.190 --> 08:35.190
Let me go.

08:35.470 --> 08:36.310
I want...

08:37.500 --> 08:38.340
Let me go.

08:38.470 --> 08:39.500
I want to gamble.

08:39.500 --> 08:40.340
Move.

08:45.660 --> 08:46.500
Let me go.

08:47.170 --> 08:48.020
Stop right there.

08:48.020 --> 08:48.860
Don't run.

09:54.660 --> 09:55.500
What is it?

09:57.070 --> 09:57.950
Where did Father go?

09:58.260 --> 09:59.740
I looked everywhere for him.

10:02.860 --> 10:04.020
Your father is the Sovereign.

10:04.260 --> 10:05.950
He has duties to bear.

10:06.500 --> 10:07.380
Once he is done,

10:07.566 --> 10:08.472
he'll come to see you.

10:09.310 --> 10:10.780
Why must Father be the Sovereign?

10:11.710 --> 10:13.660
Every time he returns to the Void,

10:14.430 --> 10:15.763
he never has time to play with me.

10:17.500 --> 10:19.540
Your father never wished for this role.

10:20.070 --> 10:21.620
He wants to stay with us.

10:22.110 --> 10:22.950
But

10:23.470 --> 10:25.110
these spirits are driven by desire.

10:25.620 --> 10:26.710
If we let those

10:26.710 --> 10:27.740
with selfish desires

10:27.740 --> 10:28.620
rule the Spirit World,

10:29.110 --> 10:30.310
it would surely throw

10:30.590 --> 10:31.950
the Mortal and Spirit Worlds

10:32.380 --> 10:33.710
into ruin and suffering.

10:36.740 --> 10:38.140
Being the Sovereign is no fun.

10:38.380 --> 10:39.660
I don't want to be the Sovereign.

10:44.900 --> 10:46.590
When you become the Sovereign one day,

10:46.900 --> 10:48.380
you will understand.

10:59.430 --> 11:00.660
(I still don't like)

11:00.660 --> 11:01.710
(to be the Sovereign.)

11:33.350 --> 11:34.190
Come on, fight.

11:35.740 --> 11:36.580
Fight.

11:37.350 --> 11:38.190
Fight!

11:39.540 --> 11:40.430
Hurry up.

11:43.230 --> 11:44.140
Simu lifted

11:44.140 --> 11:45.350
the curfew on the day

11:45.350 --> 11:46.430
of the Void Tournament

11:46.430 --> 11:47.500
and set the matches

11:47.500 --> 11:48.900
under the full moon,

11:49.190 --> 11:50.830
so these spirits

11:50.990 --> 11:52.990
would unleash their full strength.

11:53.470 --> 11:55.380
Tonight, it's only just begun.

12:00.110 --> 12:00.990
No more. I quit.

12:29.350 --> 12:30.660
Before these spirits came,

12:30.660 --> 12:32.190
they all signed death waivers.

12:32.740 --> 12:33.740
They'll fight

12:34.110 --> 12:35.470
to the death.

12:36.500 --> 12:37.340
Where is Simu?

12:37.990 --> 12:39.710
Aren't these spirits here
to challenge her?

12:42.110 --> 12:43.620
There are so many spirits

12:43.620 --> 12:44.460
vying for her seat.

12:44.590 --> 12:45.990
If Simu faces them one by one,

12:45.990 --> 12:46.830
she'll be worn out.

12:47.540 --> 12:48.620
The preliminaries

12:48.620 --> 12:49.740
started this morning.

12:50.470 --> 12:51.660
The martial contestants

12:51.830 --> 12:52.860
fight through a melee

12:53.110 --> 12:54.020
and face off in pairs.

12:54.430 --> 12:56.020
Only the final ten pairs

12:56.350 --> 12:57.310
will earn the right

12:57.310 --> 12:58.830
to face Simu directly.

13:06.500 --> 13:07.340
Everyone,

13:07.470 --> 13:09.950
the preliminaries end now.

13:20.310 --> 13:21.260
What is that smell?

13:27.830 --> 13:29.110
The time is about right.

13:29.620 --> 13:30.710
Simu should be here.

13:32.260 --> 13:33.100
Look.

13:33.100 --> 13:33.950
Quick.

13:33.950 --> 13:34.800
It's Her Grace.

13:34.800 --> 13:36.900
Her Grace is here.

13:36.900 --> 13:37.830
Her Grace.

13:37.830 --> 13:38.740
Her Grace is here.

14:17.740 --> 14:19.020
Let's not waste time.

14:19.900 --> 14:21.070
Come at me together.

14:41.470 --> 14:42.310
Your Grace,

14:42.590 --> 14:43.430
impressive!

14:43.660 --> 14:45.430
Whoever defeats me today

14:46.780 --> 14:47.740
will claim the seat

14:48.310 --> 14:49.190
of the Sovereign.

15:05.950 --> 15:07.230
I'm Wu Kui.

15:07.830 --> 15:09.020
Greetings, Your Grace.

15:09.020 --> 15:10.460
Wu Kui. He's making his move.

15:10.990 --> 15:11.830
Right now, only he

15:11.830 --> 15:12.900
can match Her Grace.

15:13.480 --> 15:14.320
Wu Kui.

15:14.320 --> 15:15.160
Wu Kui is formidable.

15:15.160 --> 15:16.350
- Exactly.
- Indeed.

15:16.350 --> 15:17.310
Watch closely.

15:17.310 --> 15:18.190
That is Wu Kui.

15:22.380 --> 15:23.470
It's been 100 years.

15:23.950 --> 15:25.230
You've grown a little stronger.

15:25.860 --> 15:26.700
Thanks, Your Grace.

15:27.380 --> 15:28.220
Then,

15:28.590 --> 15:29.430
forgive me.

15:39.260 --> 15:40.153
This spirit is strong,

15:40.473 --> 15:41.782
different from the rivals before.

15:41.860 --> 15:42.700
Of course.

15:42.860 --> 15:44.140
He was once the Lord

15:44.140 --> 15:45.590
of Zhuangling Temple.

15:46.990 --> 15:49.310
The spirits of Zhuangling Temple

15:50.990 --> 15:53.430
all crave power, especially Wu Kui.

15:54.430 --> 15:56.660
After Simu became the Sovereign,

15:57.660 --> 15:59.380
he came to challenge her
countless times.

16:00.110 --> 16:01.070
After each defeat,

16:01.070 --> 16:03.140
he resigned and went

16:03.500 --> 16:05.430
to the North Sea to train.

16:06.620 --> 16:07.950
He's not challenging Simu

16:08.260 --> 16:09.593
for the position of the Sovereign,

16:09.950 --> 16:11.470
but to become the strongest.

17:52.980 --> 17:53.820
In these 300 years,

17:53.820 --> 17:54.950
you are the first

17:55.780 --> 17:56.630
to make it this far.

17:57.150 --> 17:58.300
You flatter me.

18:27.710 --> 18:28.740
You can't beat me.

18:29.150 --> 18:30.470
Come back in the next century.

18:30.870 --> 18:31.710
Your Grace,

18:32.060 --> 18:33.300
will I be able to win

18:33.990 --> 18:35.260
in the next century?

18:41.820 --> 18:43.780
Why must you act on impulse?

18:45.580 --> 18:46.420
Your Grace,

18:47.060 --> 18:48.990
after my last defeat, I resolved

18:50.190 --> 18:51.100
that this time,

18:51.820 --> 18:52.660
I'd either prevail

18:53.500 --> 18:54.630
or perish.

18:54.990 --> 18:56.260
Spirits live long.

18:58.230 --> 18:59.300
Why would you do this?

19:00.740 --> 19:02.300
I see things differently, Your Grace.

19:03.670 --> 19:04.910
If I don't give it my all,

19:06.100 --> 19:07.820
it is no different from death.

19:08.990 --> 19:09.830
Kui.

19:39.300 --> 19:40.140
Kui!

19:41.580 --> 19:42.630
If that is your choice,

19:45.340 --> 19:47.020
I will grant your wish.

19:58.780 --> 19:59.950
Simu's Kunwu Blade.

21:00.020 --> 21:01.230
Your Grace, well done!

21:05.870 --> 21:06.710
Your Grace!

21:07.950 --> 21:08.790
Your Grace!

21:10.630 --> 21:11.470
You're incredible!

21:11.840 --> 21:12.710
Indeed.

21:12.710 --> 21:13.910
- Your Grace!
- Your Grace!

21:13.910 --> 21:14.750
I knew Simu was good,

21:15.670 --> 21:16.510
but not this good.

21:17.470 --> 21:18.780
Within ten generations,

21:18.780 --> 21:20.020
she is the strongest Sovereign.

21:20.390 --> 21:21.390
Her power is terrifying.

21:21.710 --> 21:22.580
You never saw it then.

21:23.150 --> 21:24.710
When the former Sovereign fell,

21:25.000 --> 21:26.326
the Spirits Lantern had no master,

21:26.390 --> 21:27.670
and the Void fell into chaos.

21:28.300 --> 21:29.670
In the end,

21:29.670 --> 21:31.019
Simu slew over half the rebels

21:31.030 --> 21:31.910
in the Void.

21:32.260 --> 21:33.230
Of the 24 Temples,

21:33.230 --> 21:34.670
over 30% of the Lords

21:34.670 --> 21:36.510
were annihilated by Simu.

21:36.750 --> 21:37.780
From that day on,

21:37.990 --> 21:39.100
no spirits in the Void

21:39.100 --> 21:40.470
dared tell Simu no.

21:41.340 --> 21:42.180
Of course,

21:42.740 --> 21:43.710
it includes that one.

21:57.670 --> 21:59.740
Greetings, Your Grace.

22:02.580 --> 22:03.500
Greetings, Your Grace.

22:19.100 --> 22:20.020
Only you are left now.

23:00.300 --> 23:01.430
The Chiling Secret Technique

23:01.430 --> 23:02.270
hasn't appeared

23:02.280 --> 23:03.340
for over 1,000 years.

23:15.260 --> 23:16.580
The stronger the spirit power,

23:16.910 --> 23:18.300
the harder this move hits back.

23:21.740 --> 23:23.340
The cruel part of this technique

23:23.340 --> 23:24.780
is that it drains spirit power

23:24.780 --> 23:27.300
and turns it on its owner.

23:33.780 --> 23:35.260
How generous of you.

23:35.630 --> 23:37.580
We will gladly accept it.

23:48.500 --> 23:50.710
Do you think I haven't seen

23:53.300 --> 23:54.870
this power-stealing trick?

24:06.340 --> 24:07.470
You can't withstand

24:07.470 --> 24:08.580
such overwhelming power.

24:12.230 --> 24:13.990
You're seeking death.

24:25.470 --> 24:27.630
Two annoying flies.

24:34.780 --> 24:35.780
That scent is gone.

24:37.260 --> 24:38.670
It was coming from them.

24:39.420 --> 24:42.990
♪Yet I can't♪

24:46.190 --> 24:48.150
Your Grace, you possess
supreme authority

24:48.500 --> 24:49.740
and boundless might.

24:49.990 --> 24:52.150
Your Grace, you possess
supreme authority

24:52.390 --> 24:53.870
and boundless might.

24:54.670 --> 24:57.100
Your Grace, you possess
supreme authority

24:57.260 --> 24:58.910
and boundless might.

24:59.300 --> 25:01.820
Your Grace, you possess
supreme authority

25:01.820 --> 25:03.230
and boundless might.

25:04.260 --> 25:05.100
Your Grace!

25:09.580 --> 25:10.420
Your Grace!

25:19.470 --> 25:20.310
(That scent again.)

25:30.720 --> 25:31.580
Yes.

25:31.580 --> 25:32.420
Truly astounding.

25:38.630 --> 25:40.740
This tournament now comes to an end.

25:41.150 --> 25:42.060
The Crown of the Victor

25:42.230 --> 25:44.060
still rests in the hands

25:44.190 --> 25:45.300
of the current Sovereign.

25:45.670 --> 25:47.630
All unconvinced heroes

25:47.990 --> 25:49.570
may gather

25:49.570 --> 25:50.720
in the arena

25:51.020 --> 25:52.410
and fight for the throne

25:52.490 --> 25:53.890
in another century.

26:02.390 --> 26:03.470
Enough. I know.

26:09.430 --> 26:10.270
Over here.

26:14.060 --> 26:15.020
Come, a reward.

26:15.230 --> 26:16.150
Does this feel good?

26:18.780 --> 26:19.990
It has been a while.

26:20.150 --> 26:21.190
Your touch has improved.

26:26.710 --> 26:28.030
(The scent is lost in cosmetics.)

26:32.020 --> 26:32.950
What is your name?

26:32.950 --> 26:34.190
Yes, yes.

26:34.630 --> 26:35.470
Is my touch okay?

26:35.910 --> 26:37.910
Each time you come here,

26:38.340 --> 26:40.230
you always catch me off guard.

26:40.870 --> 26:42.060
Let us have a look.

26:42.190 --> 26:43.430
You do the same to me

26:43.430 --> 26:44.540
by appearing

26:45.150 --> 26:46.260
right behind me.

26:49.390 --> 26:50.230
Yan Zhang.

26:51.950 --> 26:52.790
We are closed today.

26:53.260 --> 26:54.100
Please pardon

26:54.300 --> 26:55.150
the discourtesy.

26:57.300 --> 26:58.190
Very well.

26:58.190 --> 26:59.340
All right, all right.

27:01.340 --> 27:02.180
Lord Yan,

27:03.470 --> 27:04.820
an honored guest came.

27:05.230 --> 27:06.710
Why weren't you with him?

27:07.540 --> 27:09.470
If the ladies here get the wrong idea,

27:10.390 --> 27:11.580
can you bear that blame?

27:12.990 --> 27:14.430
I failed to notice in time

27:14.430 --> 27:15.340
that Mr. Duan was here.

27:15.710 --> 27:17.020
A grave mishap was nearly caused.

27:18.430 --> 27:20.500
Qifeng House serves ladies only.

27:21.150 --> 27:23.100
If you wish to stay and look around,

27:23.340 --> 27:25.710
please allow me to accompany you.

27:29.540 --> 27:30.380
This time,

27:30.820 --> 27:32.060
I did not come for pleasure.

27:32.670 --> 27:34.230
Then what did you come for?

27:35.100 --> 27:35.990
Young man,

27:36.260 --> 27:37.300
Qifeng House

27:37.710 --> 27:39.230
is not a place for you.

27:39.870 --> 27:41.020
But you invited me.

27:41.670 --> 27:42.630
Me?

27:42.630 --> 27:44.500
During the archery match, you said

27:45.100 --> 27:45.980
that at Xuling Temple,

27:46.740 --> 27:48.060
I could look around as I pleased.

27:50.460 --> 27:52.190
So, it seems I was in the wrong

27:52.470 --> 27:53.630
for spoiling your mood.

27:53.910 --> 27:54.990
I'm glad you remember.

27:55.780 --> 27:56.910
I almost thought

27:57.430 --> 27:58.290
I couldn't tour

27:58.290 --> 27:59.500
Xuling Temple today.

28:00.150 --> 28:01.590
After all, the tournament just ended.

28:02.190 --> 28:03.040
You must have

28:03.040 --> 28:04.820
much to handle in the aftermath.

28:16.990 --> 28:18.470
Her Grace was ambushed

28:18.470 --> 28:19.540
in the Void Valley.

28:22.230 --> 28:23.710
There is no need to worry.

28:23.870 --> 28:25.260
The Right Hand was with her.

28:25.260 --> 28:26.230
Nothing would happen.

28:27.190 --> 28:28.500
They have already returned.

28:29.260 --> 28:30.430
Simu is already

28:30.430 --> 28:31.710
resting in her bedchamber.

28:40.780 --> 28:41.620
Simu.

28:44.060 --> 28:44.900
Simu.

28:50.060 --> 28:51.200
Coming in without permission,

28:51.340 --> 28:52.620
you've grown far too bold.

28:54.020 --> 28:54.860
For the coming days,

28:55.190 --> 28:56.430
I need quiet seclusion.

28:57.195 --> 28:58.301
Go stay in the side chamber.

29:03.500 --> 29:04.340
Sir!

29:05.200 --> 29:06.060
Sir,

29:06.060 --> 29:06.900
I've been looking…

29:08.190 --> 29:09.230
for you.

29:11.950 --> 29:12.790
Her Grace…

29:13.870 --> 29:15.020
Her Grace asked me

29:15.630 --> 29:17.870
to settle you in the side chamber.

29:18.870 --> 29:20.670
Don't be too downhearted.

29:20.950 --> 29:21.960
You're so handsome.

29:21.999 --> 29:23.045
Her Grace still likes you.

29:24.230 --> 29:26.060
She just finished the tournament.

29:26.470 --> 29:28.390
So much awaits.

29:28.540 --> 29:29.380
In a few days…

29:29.580 --> 29:30.440
In a few days,

29:30.440 --> 29:31.810
she will surely summon you again.

29:36.060 --> 29:36.900
I am telling you.

29:37.190 --> 29:38.340
The side chamber is not bad.

29:38.470 --> 29:39.950
It is filled with jeweled adornments.

29:41.740 --> 29:42.580
You may go now.

29:47.670 --> 29:48.510
Yes.

29:58.300 --> 29:59.480
(Memorial)
Simu,

29:59.491 --> 30:00.850
the spirits that attacked you today

30:00.870 --> 30:01.710
are all listed here.

30:07.260 --> 30:08.609
You're in charge of the placement

30:08.620 --> 30:09.820
and ascension

30:10.260 --> 30:11.400
of the Void's spirits.

30:11.820 --> 30:12.820
Why would spirits

30:12.820 --> 30:14.310
marked as ascended on the register

30:14.740 --> 30:16.840
suddenly appear and ambush me

30:17.190 --> 30:19.100
in the Void Valley?

31:06.390 --> 31:07.820
Had you not arrived in time

31:08.230 --> 31:09.276
and fought with your life,

31:09.960 --> 31:10.820
I would not have

31:10.820 --> 31:12.020
broken free so quickly.

31:12.470 --> 31:13.310
No need for formality

31:13.470 --> 31:14.310
between us.

32:29.740 --> 32:31.190
I will look into this.

32:32.060 --> 32:33.322
If it were just the ascension

32:33.333 --> 32:34.910
that had gone awry,

32:35.610 --> 32:37.100
we'd simply deal with them by the law.

32:37.540 --> 32:39.470
But from what I saw today,

32:40.150 --> 32:41.430
those spirits were controlled.

32:41.990 --> 32:43.430
To control spirits,

32:44.540 --> 32:46.260
one must hold a fierce obsession

32:46.260 --> 32:47.100
and immense power.

32:48.710 --> 32:50.670
Someone with such an obsession

32:51.710 --> 32:53.223
and spirit power may only be the one

32:53.234 --> 32:54.330
in Nine-Square Maze Prison.

32:58.150 --> 32:58.990
It's been centuries.

33:01.630 --> 33:03.390
He was annihilated long ago.

33:05.470 --> 33:06.430
Other than him,

33:07.740 --> 33:08.870
I can think of no one else.

33:10.740 --> 33:11.950
Keep this matter quiet.

33:12.870 --> 33:14.060
Conduct the inquiry in secret.

33:14.870 --> 33:15.710
Yes.

33:17.150 --> 33:17.990
Yan,

33:19.390 --> 33:21.100
you've spent much spirit power today.

33:21.340 --> 33:22.640
Go back and get some proper rest.

33:25.990 --> 33:27.020
You should rest well too.

33:27.390 --> 33:28.500
I'll come see you tomorrow.

33:49.580 --> 33:50.910
Stop standing here in my way.

33:51.630 --> 33:53.020
Simu is in no mood

33:53.020 --> 33:53.870
to toy with you.

33:54.340 --> 33:55.180
Have some sense.

33:55.500 --> 33:57.150
Go back where you came from.

34:00.740 --> 34:01.710
Where I stay or go

34:02.670 --> 34:03.990
is not your concern.

34:09.270 --> 34:11.220
You're only her passing amusement.

34:12.500 --> 34:13.950
She already drove you out,

34:14.270 --> 34:15.750
yet you still cling to her.

34:16.540 --> 34:18.390
How shameless.

34:21.310 --> 34:22.790
You've clung to her for centuries.

34:23.790 --> 34:24.630
You are

34:24.950 --> 34:26.140
far more shameless than I am.

34:26.790 --> 34:28.310
Besides, Simu hasn't told me to leave.

34:29.500 --> 34:30.470
Who do you think you are?

34:31.270 --> 34:32.140
Who am I?

34:32.870 --> 34:34.580
I'm the Right Hand of the Void.

34:35.540 --> 34:37.100
I helped her put down the rebellion,

34:37.350 --> 34:38.470
enforced the laws,

34:38.620 --> 34:40.060
and governed the Void.

34:40.990 --> 34:42.950
I can stay by her side

34:42.950 --> 34:43.790
forever.

34:45.060 --> 34:45.900
You're just

34:48.220 --> 34:50.180
a self-righteous mortal,

34:50.750 --> 34:52.470
a shameless outsider,

34:53.330 --> 34:55.360
a useless man
who only brings Simu trouble.

34:57.830 --> 34:58.950
What can you give her?

35:46.180 --> 35:48.100
A self-righteous mortal,

35:48.870 --> 35:50.500
a shameless outsider,

35:51.500 --> 35:53.660
a useless man
who only brings Simu trouble.

35:54.910 --> 35:56.180
What can you give her?

37:10.480 --> 37:15.810
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

37:16.140 --> 37:20.390
♪Light encountered shadow♪

37:21.750 --> 37:27.120
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

37:27.420 --> 37:32.020
♪The unbreakable fate♪

37:33.110 --> 37:34.950
♪Suddenly cracked♪

37:47.160 --> 37:52.600
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

37:52.780 --> 37:57.110
♪Light encountered shadow♪

37:58.480 --> 38:03.870
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

38:04.100 --> 38:08.040
♪The unbreakable fate♪

38:09.810 --> 38:11.700
♪Suddenly cracked♪

38:14.360 --> 38:17.520
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

38:17.520 --> 38:20.050
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

38:20.050 --> 38:25.570
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

38:25.570 --> 38:28.810
♪Following fate's guidance♪

38:28.810 --> 38:33.670
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

38:34.010 --> 38:37.030
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

38:37.030 --> 38:39.850
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

38:40.110 --> 38:42.640
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

38:42.640 --> 38:48.060
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

38:48.230 --> 38:51.300
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

38:51.460 --> 38:56.360
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

38:56.570 --> 39:00.040
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
